languages.text: "Техножрецы не подпускали к нему никого, кроме блюстителей, да и тех неохотно. Джиневри, ты все время дежурила у когитатора?"
"The Tech-Priests did not let anyone near the cogitator. They even tried to prevent the enforcers' investigation. Jinevri, were you there the entire time?"

languages.text: «Los tecnosacerdotes no dejaron que nadie se acercara al cogitador, e incluso trataron de evitar la investigación de los guardias. Jinevri, ¿estuvo presente en todo momento?».

languages.text: “技术神甫禁止任何人靠近那台沉思者，他们甚至试图阻止执法者的调查。杰尼娃，你从头到尾一直都在维护室里吗？”

languages.text: 「技術司祭が誰もコジテーターに近付かせませんでした。エンフォーサーの調査さえ、防ごうとしていました。ジネヴリ、ずっとそこにいたのか？」
languages.original_text: "The Tech-Priests did not let anyone near the cogitator. They even tried to prevent the enforcers' investigation. Jinevri, were you there the entire time?"

languages.text: "Die Techpriester haben niemanden in die Nähe des Cogitators gelassen. Sie haben sogar versucht, die Ermittlung der Enforcer zu verhindern. Jinevri, wart Ihr die ganze Zeit dort?"
languages.original_text: "The Tech-Priests did not let anyone near the cogitator. They even tried to prevent the enforcers' investigation. Jinevri, were you there the entire time?"

languages.text: "Tekno Rahipler, kavramsayarın yanına kimseyi yaklaştırmadı. İnfazcıların sorgusunu engellemeye bile kalkıştılar. Jinevri, tüm bu süre boyunca sen orada mıydın?"
